are considered more authoritative and widely accepted.
<185>a<209>kara's life as given in these texts may now be summarised ç
as follows:
<185>ivaguru and °ry<193>mb<193> were a deeply pious couple belonging ç
to the well-known Namb<220>diri caste, living in K<193>la<195><200> ç
(or K<193>la<219><200>) (the modern town of Kalady in the Kerala State) ç
situated on the bank of the river P<220>r<207><193>. This childless ç
couple got <185>a<209>kara as their son after much prayer and supplication ç
